## Contact DB quick commands

DB: `~/Desktop/claude/data/contacts.db` + ChromaDB `~/Desktop/claude/data/chroma/`. Check before mentioning any person.

```bash
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/memory_search.py search "query" --top 5       # semantic
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/contacts_db.py find "Name"                    # direct
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/contacts_db.py graph "Name" 2                 # graph (depth 2)
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/contacts_db.py chain "A" "B"                  # intro chain
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/contacts_db.py stale 7                        # silent > N days
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/memory_search.py index                        # reindex ChromaDB
```

Add interaction:
```bash
python3 ~/Desktop/claude/tools/contacts_db.py sql \
  "INSERT INTO interactions (contact_id, date, type, direction, summary, source) \
   SELECT id, '{{TODAY}}', 'meeting', 'mutual', 'Summary', 'manual' \
   FROM contacts WHERE name='Name'"
```

